name: project analytics
query:
SELECT
    `tabProject`.name AS "Project name:Data:200",
    `tabChiffrage`.name AS "Chiffrage name:Data:200",
    `tabChiffrage`.risque_type AS "Risque Type:Data:150",
    `tabChiffrage`.total_project_cost AS "Total Project Cost:Data:150"
FROM
    `tabProject`
LEFT JOIN
    `tabChiffrage` ON `tabChiffrage`.project = `tabProject`.name AND `tabChiffrage`.docstatus = 1
